{"title":"革命的带路人","authors":["布巴卡尔·迪亚巴特"],"dates":[{"year":1967,"month":6,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的带路人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马里工人  布巴卡尔·迪亚巴特"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁要懂得真理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁就得学习毛主席著作。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的巨大成就，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牢记在我心里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不管走到哪里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都要宣传您那光辉的著作，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都要传播您那思想的真理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，中国的舵手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的导师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"各国革命人民的带路人。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"您不仅属于中国人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也属于非洲人民。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，世界上还存在着一批横行霸道的恶狗——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诸如那些殖民主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美帝国主义……。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渴望解放的人们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无不仰望着您。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感谢您老人家——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非洲青年的导师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界人民的救星！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}